    "README.md": [
      "# Great Wall of Legends",
      "",
      "Great Wall of Legends is a luxury showroom style web experience I built as a real client needed project for a Litty sub company focused on media walls, fireplaces, custom centerpieces, and gathering spaces that feel warm, architectural, and expensive without feeling fake.",
      "",
      "This was not just a homepage exercise to me. The brand actually needed its own front door and its own identity while still living inside the larger Litty family. I wanted the site to feel like it had a real product system, a real brand lane, and a real way for somebody to move from browsing into starting a quote. The goal was to make the project feel like a serious business presentation, not a pretty mockup with nowhere to go.",
      "",
      "## Live Site Feel",
      "",
      "The whole project is built around one idea. A fireplace wall is not just a product. It is a room anchor. So the site had to sell that feeling through layout, motion, language, and structure.",
      ""
    ],
